OL,5, A major UK leak of the extremely potent
OL,6, greenhouse gas methane has been spotted
OL,7, from space for the first time.         
OL,9,FThe leak - seen by satellite - occurred
OL,10,Fover a three-month period at a gas main
OL,11,Foperated by Wales and West Utilities.  
OL,12,FThe amount leaked could have powered   
OL,13,F7,500 homes for a year.                
OL,15,FSatellite detection shows the potential
OL,16,Fof picking up methane gas leaks quickly
OL,17,Fso they can be stopped sooner.         
OL,19,FMethane has 28 times the heating       
OL,20,Fpotential of CO2.                      
